# Per-run artifact directory.
#
# Each crop run writes here as `.claude/runs/<run_id>/`:
#   - manifest.json       — canonical run record
#   - researcher.json     — agent output
#   - drafter.json        — agent output
#   - verifier.json       — content-verifier output
#   - dispatches.jsonl    — subagent dispatch verifications
#   - decisions.jsonl     — yellow-lane auto-decisions applied
#   - handoff.md          — single human-readable summary
#
# Schema: docs/HANDOFF_FORMAT.md
# Lane policy: docs/AUTONOMY_LANES.md
#
# Per-run subdirectories are gitignored. This .gitkeep reserves the
# location and is the only file in this directory that gets committed.
